Class BimodalMutableIntSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.wala.util.intset.BimodalMutableIntSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IntSet, MutableIntSet, java.io.Serializable

    public class BimodalMutableIntSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements MutableIntSet
    An implementation of MutableIntSet that delegates to either a MutableSparseIntSet or a BitVectorIntSet
